{"tid":201440,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以入黎鬧醒我","createTime":"2017-04-14T17:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T05:38:57.000Z","uid":41670,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1589467625488b5a3944ad6b75cdd92cd0c3156","tid":201440,"uid":41670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:43:35.000Z","msg":"小弟讀緊year 1，有個拍咗拖幾年嘅女朋友<br />\n話說我同我女朋友以前同一間中學，日日都見面，大家屋企又好近所以基本上有八成時間都係一齊<br />\n但之後大家入咗唔同u，我就因為屋企同u嘅距離好遠所以選擇咗住hall<br />\n咁fall sem嘅時候都仲好地地嘅，女朋友有時會去我個hall到瞓，得閒都會出下街咁<br />\n但去到spring sem開始就出現咗啲問題，我因為莊務纏身所以平日基本上都要留係hall，有時甚至禮拜六日都冇得返屋企，但係就算返咗屋企，我女朋友都唔係話比好多時間出黎陪我，可能每個禮拜見得一兩個鐘<br />\n而且自從spring sem開始之後好多時我叫佢入黎我hall到佢都會話好遠好攰唔想黎，所以大家見面嘅時間真係少咗好多<br />\n咁同時我係hall到就識咗一個year 2女仔，咁就叫住佢做呀A先啦，呀A份人就係同咩人都可以玩得好埋嗰種人，所以我同佢都好快熟咗，基本上每晚都會係common room到一齊hea下吹下水咁<br />\n慢慢我發覺自己開始對呀A有好感，但係一黎我已經有女朋友，二黎A本身都有男朋友，三黎有一個本身同A好熟嘅組爸同我講，呀A份人係好唔識得同男仔保持距離，所以會好容易比到錯覺人<br />\n但係我仲係控制唔到自己成日都諗起佢，明明我有個一齊咗咁耐嘅女朋友就唔應該再對其他人有feel，我覺得自己真係好賤，但又冇人可以比我傾訴，有冇巴絲可以開解下我或者盡情屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7e030d9de5c07c4774d659d34a4dde2ccc0105","tid":201440,"uid":60173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:45:59.000Z","msg":"無架 飛左條女搵呀a啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"250ecf2a9c77ee6fe4655bfcfcd2695cb7dc5fda","tid":201440,"uid":65098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:47:31.000Z","msg":"分手啦廢柴 你都唔係好愛你女朋友"},{"pid":"2014442845c92b41c3830e066bcd5e28c01d6efc","tid":201440,"uid":86117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:48:11.000Z","msg":"呀A咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我就唔忍啦<br />\n日日撩佢扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e9bbfa45f63cd1906775f896132046d00d1df3","tid":201440,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:48:48.000Z","msg":"要搏盡無悔"},{"pid":"61d33b79f948410519b7989004fc855bfc9f1be9","tid":201440,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"錯覺嚟嘅啫 <br />\n盡量同返女朋友傾吓計<br />\n關心吓<br />\n可能呢一切都可以解決㗎喇"},{"pid":"d98740796309efb8cd79e836248f454656f95b9e","tid":201440,"uid":106130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:50:10.000Z","msg":"一時新鮮感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f538e079daa30f28b9dfa358fdaf76385ecd2251","tid":201440,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:54:30.000Z","msg":"唔好分手 但偷偷撩a扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9933ca494b3207eec62a27d88553f82670012d2","tid":201440,"uid":41670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手啦廢柴 你都唔係好愛你女朋友</blockquote><br />\n但由中學到而家4,5年，就算撇除愛情呢個因素，我都仲係好想我女朋友可以繼續出現係我生命中，可能真係習慣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa3deecb73e3cd1e95c84d36649f0d922d7c4ce","tid":201440,"uid":41670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:00:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀A咁正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比我就唔忍啦<br />\n日日撩佢扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔係啲咁嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢本身又有男朋友，同埋佢係真係當我係好朋友先至同我咁close，佢係好男仔性格嗰種女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4badbddca576c5d063c763361607fc986588b41","tid":201440,"uid":41670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:02:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>錯覺嚟嘅啫 <br />\n盡量同返女朋友傾吓計<br />\n關心吓<br />\n可能呢一切都可以解決㗎喇</blockquote><br />\n我都好想同女朋友傾下大家淡咗呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔知係咪大家太了解對方所以真係好難開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋佢好似唔覺得而家呢種相處方式有問題咁"},{"pid":"a33dc4ba5018a95e3b2c13c609938fc5ff089b63","tid":201440,"uid":88235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"扮搵a傾心事 灌醉佢上床<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ba1965b620dd0bf46a72a4ffc4a293a3dcff31","tid":201440,"uid":1444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T20:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551061a5512986fae3f333cb2633ed7a1e6040c3","tid":201440,"uid":77148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T23:05:53.000Z","msg":"仆街四步曲<br />\n新屎坑三日香<br />\n人不風流枉少年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一失足成千古恨<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">他朝君體也相同</span>"},{"pid":"edcedc7d4779a6722aa38b9a6bf45b2278998865","tid":201440,"uid":106130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>錯覺嚟嘅啫 <br />\n盡量同返女朋友傾吓計<br />\n關心吓<br />\n可能呢一切都可以解決㗎喇</blockquote><br />\n我都好想同女朋友傾下大家淡咗呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但唔知係咪大家太了解對方所以真係好難開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋佢好似唔覺得而家呢種相處方式有問題咁</blockquote><br />\n傾下啦，我同男友都係，不過得我覺得淡，佢仲係熱戀期咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢有盡力去維持返，唔好咁易放棄咁耐維持既感情，就算比你同左a一齊總有日都係會覺得淡同埋習慣左對方會好似親人既關係"},{"pid":"f87f3ea1551db74be26a972dd5f905b0a6876c1b","tid":201440,"uid":70182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017